column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SOFT GUM TROPICAL TWIST 81 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050074877
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sweeteners (sorbitol, xylitol, maltitol, maltitol syrup, aspartame, sucralose, acesulfame K), gum base, flavourings, acids (citric, malic), humectant (glycerol), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), colour (paprika extract), antioxidant (E321). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine. Date available: 02/23/2018 Date last updated by company: 02/23/2018
